However, the importance of physical exercise should not be underestimated.
Those who exercise regularly reduce their chances of developing cancer or depression.
Physical activity helps with weight correction, high blood pressure, diabetes, and yet a long list of benefits, too long to bring here.
But the beauty of Pokémon Go is that it draws people out to do what they love.
