Some people even make new friends on the hunt.
As usual, there are boring boredoms who are looking for something to complain about.
And yes, someone might stumble on the door.
Well, what?
The breakthrough happened.
After all, even though smartphone apps like Fitbit could still track our physical activity in the past, they didn’t give us a reason to practice, as this game does.
The novelty will come, and the use will weaken over time.
However, due to the success of Pokemon, there will be more games that will combine applications and virtual reality with physical activity in the real world, helping many people on the hunt to be more active, in good shape and healthy.
