Notifications on transport tax will stop sending by mail - website Driving www.zr.ru
The Tax Inspectorate has changed the procedure for sending notifications of property taxes.
All Russian car owners are accustomed to the system that has not changed over the years: in the summer and autumn, they receive receipts for payment of transport tax for the previous year.
This year, however, many will not be able to attend.
The fact is that the tax inspection without too much noise changed the procedure for notifying citizens.
Those who are registered in the "Personal office of the taxpayer" on the official website of the department nalog.ru, notifications will come in electronic form.
The inspection automatically identified such Russians as online users and deleted them from the standard, "paper" mailing list.
The news will affect all owners of vehicles and real estate.
All the others will still receive the usual letters.
However, the opportunity to return to the old scheme is also available to the account holders on the site.
To do this, they will have to visit the tax office during August and write an application.
On the one hand, the new order is more modern and convenient.
The notification will appear in the "personal office" immediately after compilation, while the letter will go a few days and may be lost at all.
In addition, the number of users of the Internet service of the tax inspection exceeded 18 million people, which will allow the department to seriously save on the mailing.
On the other hand, the modest news on the inspection website is clearly not enough to inform citizens about the changed order.
Some could register in the "personal office" to receive a one-time service and have long forgotten about it.
These people will not wait for notifications by mail and, without knowing it, will fall into the category of non-payers with all the resulting consequences.
Access to the "Personal Office of the taxpayer" is carried out in three ways: through the account of the portal gosuslugi.ru, using an electronic signature or by entering the login and password specified in the registration card.
The latter can be obtained personally at any tax inspection office (regardless of the place of registration).
We would like to remind you that this year the transport tax must be paid before December 1.
Notifications began in July.
